{"tid":1517863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"任何人都可以係集會發起人","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:04:08.000Z","uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64ce8dae1375533aa62e581395316bb1b9c08f24","tid":1517863,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:01:47.000Z","msg":"steps:<br />\n1. 向黑警申請<br />\n2. 重點：佢批又好唔批又好，<span style=\"color: red;\">發起人唔好出現</span>； 佢批，你詐肚痛唔黎，佢唔批，宣佈取消<br />\n3. 重點之二：由發起集會果一刻，文宣已經要開turbo瘋狂宣傳，就算發起人之後宣佈取消，龐大群眾赴會既意識已經成型，當日既集會地點同時間已成定局<br />\n4. 之後集會發展成點，身為發起人既你冇出現過，咩都冇講過，黑警搵唔到位入你<br />\n<br />\n班on9仲以為拉哂班發起人就鎮壓到場革命"},{"pid":"fc8a471aae8bcb728514e4b90ad608ce27cec74e","tid":1517863,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9e64643821f10142e6aa2fec02ce0c4a617d0a","tid":1517863,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"天真"}]}